V0410_01_00_00_0.text: Which of my fabulous fans should I take on today?

V0410_01_00_01_0.text:
Sure, let's Duel.
I never want to disappoint a fan.

V0410_01_00_02_0.text: I get a thrill out of spoiling my fans!

V0410_01_00_04_0.text:
Want my autograph now?
Cuz you won't get one after you lose.

V0410_01_00_05_0.text:
What's wrong, Shark?
Forget the face of your #1 fan?

V0410_01_00_08_0.text:
Ooh, you have a Number.
This should be fun.

V0410_03_00_00_0.text: I won't be happy until my fans get what they deserve!

V0410_03_00_01_0.text: You won't like what's coming next!

V0410_03_00_02_0.text: I hope you're enjoying our one-on-one time!

V0410_03_00_04_0.text: Stop spoiling my plans, you little twerp!

V0410_03_00_05_0.text:
You've made me angry!
And now you'll pay!

V0410_05_00_00_0.text: Not only do I have luck on my side, I also have skill!

V0410_06_01_01_0.text: If you're going to do that...

V0410_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0410_11_01_00_0.text: I summon a monster in defense position!

V0410_11_08_01_0.text:
I build the Overlay Network!
Xyz Summon!

V0410_14_00_01_0.text:
Want to know how I treat my fans?
Let's battle!

V0410_15_00_02_0.text: There's bad news coming your way!

V0410_16_00_00_0.text: Our meet-and-greet is coming to an end!

V0410_16_00_01_0.text: This is the end of the line for you!

V0410_21_00_00_1.text:
You look scared.
I love it!

V0410_21_00_01_0.text: You've done well to survive, but not enough to win!

V0410_21_00_04_1.text: Why do you refuse to lose?

V0410_21_00_05_0.text: You're starting to get on my nerves!

V0410_28_00_00_0.text:
Your Dueling was awesome.
Just not as good as mine!

V0410_28_00_01_0.text: I don't know how it was for you, but I enjoyed this Duel.

V0410_28_00_01_1.text: Especially the part where I watched you squirm!

V0410_28_00_02_0.text:
Have you become my fan?
Hahahahaha!

V0410_28_00_03_0.text: You look so sad... which is exactly what I wanted to see!

V0410_28_00_03_1.text: I give a lot to my fans, so it's nice when they give back!

V0410_28_00_05_0.text: Believe me when I say that this isn't what I wanted.

V0410_29_00_00_0.text:
Argh...
I'm done being nice to my fans!

V0410_29_00_02_0.text: I’ll pay you back double for this!

V0410_29_00_03_0.text: This is what I get for being a people pleaser.

V0410_29_00_04_0.text:
Shark...
I'm sorry for what I did to you...

V0410_29_00_05_0.text: Instead of being mad at the world, just be mad at me.

V0410_29_00_08_0.text: If today's not the day, maybe you can forgive me someday.

V0410_33_00_00_0.text: A star is nothing without his fans!

V0410_30_00_00_0.text: Let me Duel the way I want!

V0410_30_00_01_0.text: That's not good enough to defeat me!

V0410_30_00_02_0.text: I enjoy turning your smile into a frown.

V0410_34_00_01_0.text: If you're really my fan, stop countering my moves!

V0410_34_00_02_0.text:
I won't accept your surrender.
So stand up!

V0410_34_00_03_0.text: You actually fell for my trap?

V0410_34_00_04_0.text: There's this thing called a brain. Learn to use it.

V0410_34_00_05_0.text: I can't believe you'd resort to those tricks!

V0410_34_00_06_0.text: You need to strike hard like I do!

V0410_34_00_09_0.text: Nothing but the best for my fans!

V0410_35_00_00_0.text: I won't let my fans down!

V0410_35_00_01_0.text: I'll gladly do anything for my fans!

V0410_36_00_00_0.text:
Humph...
Just when it was getting to the good part.

V0410_36_00_02_0.text: Make sure I get another turn!

V0410_36_00_03_0.text: This is no time to be nice, Trey!

V0410_36_00_04_0.text:
I'm the one who'll defeat them, not you!
Got it, Trey?

V0410_36_00_06_0.text: You should have no problems if you Duel as well as I do.

V0410_36_00_07_0.text: This should be easy for you, Shark!

V0410_27_00_00_0.text: You have to be kidding me!

V0410_08_00_00_0.text: I activate Rank-Up-Magic Argent Chaos Force!

V0410_08_00_00_1.text: My brother put his heart and soul into this card!

V0410_08_00_01_0.text: I activate Rank-Up-Magic Argent Chaos Force!

V0410_08_00_01_1.text: It ranks up my Xyz Monster to a CXyz!

V0410_08_00_02_0.text: I activate Argent Chaos Force's effect from my Graveyard!

V0410_08_00_02_1.text: This card reminds me that Duels are a lot more than winning!

V0410_08_00_03_0.text: I activate Argent Chaos Force's effect from my Graveyard!

V0410_08_00_03_1.text: I return this card to my hand!

V0410_08_00_04_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Puppet Ritual!

V0410_08_00_04_1.text: It revives two Level 8 Gimmick Puppets from my Graveyard!

V0410_08_00_05_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Condolence Puppet!

V0410_08_00_06_0.text: Condolence Puppet's effect activates from my Graveyard!

V0410_08_00_06_1.text: The monster I choose can't be destroyed by your effects!

V0410_08_00_07_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Junk Puppet!

V0410_08_00_07_1.text: It Special Summons a Gimmick Puppet from my Graveyard! Rise!

V0410_08_00_08_0.text: I activate the Continuous Spell, Perform Puppet!

V0410_08_00_09_0.text: I banish a Gimmick Puppet to activate Perform Puppet!

V0410_08_00_09_1.text: My monsters now have the same Level as the banished monster!

V0410_08_00_10_0.text: When Gimmick Puppet is destroyed, Perform Puppet activates!

V0410_08_00_10_1.text: It Special Summons a banished Gimmick Puppet!

V0410_08_00_11_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Puppet Parade!

V0410_08_00_12_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Xyz Effect!

V0410_08_00_12_1.text: It destroys one card on the field!

V0410_08_00_13_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Marshalling Field!

V0410_08_00_15_0.text: Marshalling Field activates when it's sent to the Graveyard!

V0410_08_00_15_1.text: I add Rank-Up-Magic Argent Chaos Force to my hand!

V0410_08_00_16_0.text: Here's a little taste of what's to come.

V0410_08_00_16_1.text:
I activate my Trap!
Mirror Force!

V0410_08_00_17_1.text: I activate the Continuous Trap, Skill Drain!

V0410_08_00_18_1.text: I activate the Field Spell, Necrovalley!

V0410_09_00_00_0.text: Giant Grinder uses 1 Overlay Unit to destroy your monster!

V0410_09_00_00_1.text: Aren't you glad to be my fan?

V0410_09_00_01_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Giant Grinder's effect!

V0410_09_00_02_0.text: Gimmick Puppet of Strings's effect activates!

V0410_09_00_02_1.text: It puts a String Counter on all other monsters!

V0410_09_00_03_0.text: Gimmick Puppet of Strings's effect activates!

V0410_09_00_04_0.text: My Gimmick Puppet controls the strings of fate!

V0410_09_00_04_1.text: Destroy all monsters with String Counters and deal damage!

V0410_09_00_05_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate my Leo's effect!

V0410_09_00_05_1.text: When it has 3 Destiny Counters, I win the Duel!

V0410_09_00_06_0.text:
As of this moment, I win!
My Number is unstoppable!

V0410_09_00_07_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate my Giant Hunter's effect!

V0410_09_00_07_1.text:
It destroys a card.
And if it's a monster, you take damage!

V0410_09_00_08_0.text: Dark Strings destroys all monsters with String Counters!

V0410_09_00_09_0.text: Dark Strings uses 1 Overlay Unit to activate its effect!

V0410_09_00_09_1.text: All your face-up monsters gain a String Counter!

V0410_09_00_10_0.text: Disaster Leo uses an Overlay Unit to deal you damage!

V0410_09_00_11_1.text: Because Disaster Leo has Gimmick Puppet of Leo's powers!

V0410_09_00_12_0.text: I use 2 Overlay Units to activate Gigantes Doll's effect!

V0410_09_00_12_1.text: I take control of up to two of your monsters this turn!

V0410_09_00_13_1.text: I Tribute this card to change all my monsters to Level 8!

V0410_09_00_15_0.text: Scissor Arms sends a Gimmick Puppet in my deck to the Grave!

V0410_09_00_16_0.text: When I take direct damage, Shadow Feeler's effect activates!

V0410_09_00_16_1.text: I Special Summon it from my Graveyard, but I take damage!

V0410_09_00_17_0.text: When I summon Terror Baby, I can resurrect a Gimmick Puppet!

V0410_09_00_18_0.text: I banish Terror Baby from my Graveyard to use its effect!

V0410_09_00_18_1.text: You can't play effects against my Gimmick Puppets' effects!

V0410_09_00_19_0.text: I activate Twilight Joker's effect from my hand!

V0410_09_00_19_1.text: I banish my destroyed Gimmick Puppet to Special Summon it!

V0410_09_00_20_0.text: When my Nightmare is Special Summoned, its effect activates!

V0410_09_00_20_1.text: I Special Summon another copy from my hand or Graveyard!

V0410_09_00_21_0.text: Dreary Doll's effect activates from my Graveyard!

V0410_09_00_21_1.text: I revive it by banishing a Gimmick Puppet from my Graveyard!

V0410_09_00_22_1.text: When it's summoned, it brings another Gimmick Puppet along!

V0410_09_00_23_0.text: Bisque Doll's effect activates from my Graveyard!

V0410_09_00_23_1.text: Your effects can't target my Gimmick Puppets this turn!

V0410_09_00_25_0.text: I discard a Gimmick Puppet to deal you damage!

V0410_09_00_26_0.text: I discard a Gimmick Puppet to change this card to Level 8!

V0410_09_00_27_0.text: Gimmick Puppet Des Troy's effect activates!

V0410_09_00_27_1.text: It destroys one Gimmick Puppet on the field!

V0410_09_00_28_0.text: When Des Troy is a goner, I can summon 2 Gimmick Puppets!

V0410_37_00_00_1.text: The puppet that controls the strings of fate!

V0410_13_00_01_0.text:
Appear!
Number 40: Gimmick Puppet of Strings!

V0410_13_00_02_0.text:
This is the true ace in my deck!
Number 88!

V0410_37_00_02_0.text:
Chaos Xyz Evolution!
Argh... Let's go!
Number C15!

V0410_37_00_02_1.text: Rip up the strings of destiny!

V0410_37_00_03_0.text:
Chaos Xyz Evolution!
Here comes Number C40!

V0410_37_00_03_1.text: The wisdom of the world brings you to this realm!

V0410_37_00_04_0.text:
Chaos Xyz Evolution!
Say hello to Number C88!

V0410_37_00_04_1.text: Let your roar bring destruction upon the world!

V0410_13_00_05_0.text: Number C88: Gimmick Puppet Disaster Leo!

V0410_13_00_09_0.text:
Come on out!
Gimmick Puppet Shadow Feeler!

V0410_13_00_15_0.text: Join me, Gimmick Puppet Bisque Doll!

V0410_13_00_17_0.text: Here comes Gimmick Puppet Magnet Doll!

V0410_13_00_19_0.text:
I'll play this card.
Gravekeeper's Descendant!

V0410_19_00_01_0.text:
Gimmick Puppet of Strings!
Cut 'em down to size!

V0410_19_00_02_0.text: Leo! Slice anyone who stands in your way!

V0410_19_00_03_0.text: Giant Hunter! Show some love to our biggest fan!

V0410_19_00_11_0.text: Gimmick Puppet Twilight Joker! Go get 'em!
